title: 12/23/21 DPS Best Of

description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Brady Quinn to preview the College Football Playoffs. Who does he have winning it all? Mr. Christmas Michael Buble calls in to serenade Mclovin and judge Fritzy's singing. And McLovin bids farewell on his final DP Show ever.
